Join your fellow Kentico experts, enthusiasts, or anyone who wants to learn about Kentico in downtown Milwaukee, WI on Thursday December 7.
:::note Date: 2023/12/7
Time: 5:00-7:00 PM CST
Location: 219 N Milwaukee St, Milwaukee, WI 53202, 2nd floor. :::
Register for the event and see [all the details on Meetup.com](https://www.meetup.com/mkekug/events/297418075/) or the [LinkedIn post](https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7138234633602666496/)
If you would like to see a Kentico user group start in your area, [let us know](https://community.kentico.com/#gridsection-feedback).
